webpackJsonp([0x8af8c5da91a6],{"./node_modules/json-loader/index.js!./.cache/json/mutekabiliyet.json":function(e,a){e.exports={data:{site:{siteMetadata:{author:"Burak Tokak",description:"SaaS, e-ticaret ve diğer dijital ürünlerinizin verimini arttırmak için kullanabileceğiniz ücretsiz ve örneklerle destekli bir psikolojik prensip kütüphanesidir.",facebookAppId:"310591556081648",title:"Dijital Psikoloji",twitterHandle:"danistefanovic",siteUrl:"https://dijitalpsikoloji.com"}},markdownRemark:{html:'<p><em>“Eğer yeterince insana istediklerini elde etmeleri için yardım edersen, hayatta istediğin her şeyi elde edebilirsin.”</em> Zig Ziglar</p>\n<p>Bize iyilik yapan insanlara iyilik yapmak gibi bir sorumluluğumuz olduğunu hissederiz. Bu kural tanıdığınız veya sosyal çevrenizdekiler için geçerliyken, tanımadığınız insanlar için de geçerlidir. Bu insanların topluluklar halinde yaşamasını sağlayan bir karakteristiktir (<a href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/2092623?seq=1#page_scan_tab_contents">Gouldner, 1960</a>).</p>\n<h2>Studies</h2>\n<p>In an experiment by <a href="http://www.communicationcache.com/uploads/1/0/8/8/10887248/effects_of_a_favor_and_liking_on_compliance.pdf">Regan (1971)</a>, a subject thought that they were evaluating art. Also in the room was a fellow participant, who was, in reality, a research assistant. In one condition, the assistant would leave the room and bring back two cans of Coke – for him and the subject. In another condition, he would return empty-handed. At the end of the experiment, the assistant asked the participants if they would buy a raffle ticket from him. As expected, the subjects who had received the gift were twice as likely to purchase tickets, even though the tickets were far more expensive than the can of soda had been.</p>\n<p>Reciprocity outperforms reward as a principle of persuasion when it comes to collecting correct contact information from a user. According to <a href="https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007%252F978-3-540-77006-0_24">Gamberini, Petrucci, Spoto and Spagnolli (2007</a>), asking for contact details, which would unlock a link to a whitepaper (reward) generated slightly more entries, but most of them were invalid; whereas providing the whitepaper for free and then asking for contact information for further news (reciprocity) led to less entries, but more valid ones overall.</p>\n<p>Even very inexpensive meals (&#x3C; $20) sponsored by pharmaceutical firms led to an increase in physician prescriptions of the promoted brand-name medication, even when a generic equivalent was available (<a href="http://jamanetwork.com/journals/jamainternalmedicine/article-abstract/2528290">DeJong et al., 2016</a>).</p>\n<h2>Examples</h2>\n<h3>Guest blogging</h3>\n<p>Write unique and high-quality posts for other blogs, of which they can be proud. To give back, they will be more likely to promote the content more vigorously, or offer to write something on your blog in return. It’s not unusual for an outstanding guest post to result in a long-standing partnership.</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 550px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 56.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="Reciprocity Example: Guest blogging"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/f3846c0a36b1413851ca335c116b4752-bf077.png"\n        srcset="/static/f3846c0a36b1413851ca335c116b4752-235b1.png 138w,\n/static/f3846c0a36b1413851ca335c116b4752-730c0.png 275w,\n/static/f3846c0a36b1413851ca335c116b4752-bf077.png 550w,\n/static/f3846c0a36b1413851ca335c116b4752-b4be9.png 825w,\n/static/f3846c0a36b1413851ca335c116b4752-8a14d.png 1100w,\n/static/f3846c0a36b1413851ca335c116b4752-9dd46.png 1200w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<h3>Gifts in social games</h3>\n<p>All gifting mechanisms in social games like FarmVille or Mafia Wars where a user can send in-game items to a friend, rely on the principle of reciprocity. If I send you something, wouldn’t you send me something back?</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 550px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 56.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAALCAYAAAB/Ca1DAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAdklEQVQoz+2SOwqAMBBEbQQl/iKGEBD0dPkH0uX6zoKNnQp2DjyW3eIxgVTVn0/ivZfW2s4Yo8CKSJw3sOC+gxHI20JIRAhhJqHWmpMI8BMSK8ZY/7gpidFEOOcGtJ5ijD2meP30nHMDSZNSqgnsbSml/j/FJQd2JR9gC5L4TQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="Reciprocity Example: Gifts in social games"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/6d8fd3369bb5df76563f47a0805c2db1-bf077.png"\n        srcset="/static/6d8fd3369bb5df76563f47a0805c2db1-235b1.png 138w,\n/static/6d8fd3369bb5df76563f47a0805c2db1-730c0.png 275w,\n/static/6d8fd3369bb5df76563f47a0805c2db1-bf077.png 550w,\n/static/6d8fd3369bb5df76563f47a0805c2db1-b4be9.png 825w,\n/static/6d8fd3369bb5df76563f47a0805c2db1-8a14d.png 1100w,\n/static/6d8fd3369bb5df76563f47a0805c2db1-9dd46.png 1200w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<h3>Asking for app ratings</h3>\n<p>First and foremost: build a great app. Once that requirement is met, make sure that a positive experience exists before asking a user to rate your app, e.g. after a booking, purchase, or being a loyal user for several days.</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 550px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 56.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAALCAYAAAB/Ca1DAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAYklEQVQoz2NgGAU0A/39/UzZ2dmsRUVFLEAuT0lJCTMQs6SlpbHX1dUxkWxgbm4uS1ZWFm9GRoYkkCsMNFwgPT2dB2igZHd3NyNZrszMzJQDGioCxKJAA/mBfAmoBaOAhgAAA/YbO+dXueYAAAAASUVORK5CYII=\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="Reciprocity Example: Asking for app ratings"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/a0481e23ede1d7127c34f5683ce0e824-bf077.png"\n        srcset="/static/a0481e23ede1d7127c34f5683ce0e824-235b1.png 138w,\n/static/a0481e23ede1d7127c34f5683ce0e824-730c0.png 275w,\n/static/a0481e23ede1d7127c34f5683ce0e824-bf077.png 550w,\n/static/a0481e23ede1d7127c34f5683ce0e824-b4be9.png 825w,\n/static/a0481e23ede1d7127c34f5683ce0e824-8a14d.png 1100w,\n/static/a0481e23ede1d7127c34f5683ce0e824-9dd46.png 1200w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<h3>10x content marketing</h3>\n<p>Give away value in the form of free, kick-ass blog posts, webinars, ebooks, whitepapers, videos, mini-applications, and so on. People got used to receiving mediocre freebies, and you’re expected to give everything away nowadays. It’s rarely perceived as a favor. Create something that is ten times better than the best result you can find on your topic. When your content enables someone to yield results, they are more likely to give back by sharing it, or even becoming a paying customer. What about asking for an email address before giving access to the content? No, that’s not a reciprocity-invoking tactic.</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 550px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 56.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAALCAYAAAB/Ca1DAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAALUlEQVQoz2NgGAVDB2RkZEilpaUJp6enSwHZspmZmfxAWhhIywOleUdDaAgBACH7CTiAT0RLAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="Reciprocity Example: 10x content marketing"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/224948c764ce0cfaa44919a6982de716-bf077.png"\n        srcset="/static/224948c764ce0cfaa44919a6982de716-235b1.png 138w,\n/static/224948c764ce0cfaa44919a6982de716-730c0.png 275w,\n/static/224948c764ce0cfaa44919a6982de716-bf077.png 550w,\n/static/224948c764ce0cfaa44919a6982de716-b4be9.png 825w,\n/static/224948c764ce0cfaa44919a6982de716-8a14d.png 1100w,\n/static/224948c764ce0cfaa44919a6982de716-9dd46.png 1200w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<h3>Showing your face in cold emails</h3>\n<p>In a study, subjects were requested to fill out a survey, which they received by email. Attaching a sender’s photograph at the end of the email increased the compliance rate (<a href="http://online.liebertpub.com/doi/abs/10.1089/109493102753770525">Guéguen &#x26; Jacob, 2004</a>). That’s exactly what Stephen Twomey did in <a href="https://justreachout.io/blog/howto-increase-response-rate-email-pitch/">an experiment</a> where he pitched his guest posts. He increased the response rate with this technique by 333.33%.</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 550px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 56.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAALCAYAAAB/Ca1DAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAQ0lEQVQoz2NgGAU0BWlpadzp6ekKmZmZIlQxMDc3lwNooDzQQFEgFs/IyJCh1ExWIGYGYjYg5qCGI5mgmAVKjwJMAADMowqbP1fl1gAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="Reciprocity Example: Showing your face in cold emails"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/d48acbfa59ebc1686ad9edc7a4712245-bf077.png"\n        srcset="/static/d48acbfa59ebc1686ad9edc7a4712245-235b1.png 138w,\n/static/d48acbfa59ebc1686ad9edc7a4712245-730c0.png 275w,\n/static/d48acbfa59ebc1686ad9edc7a4712245-bf077.png 550w,\n/static/d48acbfa59ebc1686ad9edc7a4712245-b4be9.png 825w,\n/static/d48acbfa59ebc1686ad9edc7a4712245-8a14d.png 1100w,\n/static/d48acbfa59ebc1686ad9edc7a4712245-9dd46.png 1200w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<h3>Building trust by breaking anonymity</h3>\n<p>Use the same principle in other areas to increase the likelihood of reciprocity: add an author box to each blog post, show the faces behind your brand on your social media accounts, or create an “About Us” page for your product. Trust and reciprocity often go hand-in-hand (<a href="http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0899825685710275">Berg, Dickhaut &#x26; McCabe, 1995</a>).</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 550px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 56.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAALCAYAAAB/Ca1DAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAgElEQVQoz+2R0QrCIABFx6JiscYYjWoFRvRtKr7o/6mgz/7UzqDXXmKPu3A4F9H7YlVtWS0xxjal9II+hHDPOY/ee1FKOfy7uYcdHKGx1p6UUr2UcsIjfuOb1rozxnT4A4Lz56/B+ssyWnPxzMDEowt9oC++4gcMdOGca7a/XT8z76EryP4LXi0AAAAASUVORK5CYII=\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="Reciprocity Example: Building trust by breaking anonymity"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/1df54214cb23d37b62ad01be4d3c7fb5-bf077.png"\n        srcset="/static/1df54214cb23d37b62ad01be4d3c7fb5-235b1.png 138w,\n/static/1df54214cb23d37b62ad01be4d3c7fb5-730c0.png 275w,\n/static/1df54214cb23d37b62ad01be4d3c7fb5-bf077.png 550w,\n/static/1df54214cb23d37b62ad01be4d3c7fb5-b4be9.png 825w,\n/static/1df54214cb23d37b62ad01be4d3c7fb5-8a14d.png 1100w,\n/static/1df54214cb23d37b62ad01be4d3c7fb5-9dd46.png 1200w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<h3>Free coaching sessions</h3>\n<p>This act works like the previously-mentioned content marketing freebies, but instead of being anonymous, the attendee has to put away his anonymity. A study shows that people who received a favor and were required to put their contact information on a pledge card were more likely to comply with the donation request (<a href="https://www.researchgate.net/publication/247808309_The_Effect_of_a_Favor_on_Public_and_Private_Compliance_How_Internalized_is_the_Norm_of_Reciprocity">Whatley, Webster, Smith &#x26; Rhodes, 1999</a>).</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 550px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 56.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAALCAYAAAB/Ca1DAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAeUlEQVQoz2NgGAVUB+np6Vw5OTlsRUVF7JWVlazt7e3MGRkZHCCxgoICEJsNyOYAsjmysrLY169fz4jXwOzsbEGgJjEgFgZq5ElJSeHLz8/nBvJFgZbxpKamigNpgczMTBEgFiLVwaxALAbEIkAM0iwNxCyj8UhbAABuESHj586GlwAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="Reciprocity Example: Free coaching sessions"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/047d91fefd4c57e0ce156fa12b10d086-bf077.png"\n        srcset="/static/047d91fefd4c57e0ce156fa12b10d086-235b1.png 138w,\n/static/047d91fefd4c57e0ce156fa12b10d086-730c0.png 275w,\n/static/047d91fefd4c57e0ce156fa12b10d086-bf077.png 550w,\n/static/047d91fefd4c57e0ce156fa12b10d086-b4be9.png 825w,\n/static/047d91fefd4c57e0ce156fa12b10d086-8a14d.png 1100w,\n/static/047d91fefd4c57e0ce156fa12b10d086-9dd46.png 1200w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<h3>Messaging</h3>\n<p>Following the reciprocity rule, when a user gets a message within Whatsapp, Facebook, Snapchat, or elsewhere, the recipient is somewhat obligated to send something back. In Snapchat, this effect is increased even more because “Snaps” disappear in seconds. You need to reply promptly before you forget what you got.</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 550px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 56.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="Reciprocity Example: Messaging"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/4f7bb63463d017409b860163a0bf7625-bf077.png"\n        srcset="/static/4f7bb63463d017409b860163a0bf7625-235b1.png 138w,\n/static/4f7bb63463d017409b860163a0bf7625-730c0.png 275w,\n/static/4f7bb63463d017409b860163a0bf7625-bf077.png 550w,\n/static/4f7bb63463d017409b860163a0bf7625-b4be9.png 825w,\n/static/4f7bb63463d017409b860163a0bf7625-8a14d.png 1100w,\n/static/4f7bb63463d017409b860163a0bf7625-9dd46.png 1200w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>',fields:{path:"/mutekabiliyet/",slug:"mutekabiliyet"},frontmatter:{datePublished:"2017-09-11T08:15:15Z",title:"Mütekabiliyet",seoImage:{childImageSharp:{resize:{src:"/static/61f7e5eae4ba9726dc64886ac7431add-a159b.png"}}}}},allMarkdownRemark:{edges:[{node:{fields:{path:"/adanma-sureklilik/",slug:"adanma-sureklilik"},frontmatter:{title:"Adanma ve Süreklilik"}}},{node:{fields:{path:"/az-bulunurluk/",slug:"az-bulunurluk"},frontmatter:{title:"Az Bulunurluk"}}},{node:{fields:{path:"/capalanmislik/",slug:"capalanmislik"},frontmatter:{title:"Çapalanmışlık"}}},{node:{fields:{path:"/kayip-kahri/",slug:"kayip-kahri"},frontmatter:{title:"Kayıp Kahrı"}}},{node:{fields:{path:"/mutekabiliyet/",slug:"mutekabiliyet"},frontmatter:{title:"Mütekabiliyet"}}},{node:{fields:{path:"/odullendirme/",slug:"odullendirme"},frontmatter:{title:"Ödüllendirme"}}},{node:{fields:{path:"/sosyal-dayanak/",slug:"sosyal-dayanak"},frontmatter:{title:"Sosyal Dayanak"}}},{node:{fields:{path:"/tamamlama-ihtiyaci/",slug:"tamamlama-ihtiyaci"},frontmatter:{title:"Tamamlama İhtiyacı"}}},{node:{fields:{path:"/tetikleyiciler/",slug:"tetikleyiciler"},frontmatter:{title:"Tetikleyiciler"}}}]}},pathContext:{path:"/mutekabiliyet/",slug:"mutekabiliyet"}}}});
